data.description: Due to a sensitive family matter,  the buyer terminated the contract. The home is officially Back on the Market! Less than 2 years old! BETTER THAN NEW ~ blinds added, stainless refrigerator, fans/lighting added, plus ALL interior walls, trim and doors repainted in Sep 2023, bedroom carpets professionally cleaned as well.  LITERALLY move-in ready.   Easy to show.  Available for a quick closing.  Open and spacious floorplan, granite, tile, lvp, gas stove, built-in microwave, large laundry room, and two car garage with opener.  Don't miss this one!  Relaxing covered patio backs to wooded lot and offers a view of the pond.  No tricks nor gimmicks, just a great home offered at a really great price.
